  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"My Waifu Becomes Real\"</strong> is an immersive interactive visual novel that blurs the lines between fantasy and reality. Step into the life of an anime enthusiast whose dreams come true when Laras, his beloved waifu, becomes real and starts living with him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a story filled with humor, warmth, and heart-fluttering moments as you navigate the joys and challenges of living with a waifu who’s charming, quirky, and full of surprises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/882786b3861e6b0115414731ff05f04d.poster.avif?t=1743995851\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/882786b3861e6b0115414731ff05f04d.webm?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/882786b3861e6b0115414731ff05f04d.mp4?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet Laras<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/aef005d297d275e4d6e9570d97c38cb4.avif?t=1743995851\" width=800 height=929 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sweet and Caring</strong>: Always ready to brighten your day with her infectious energy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playful and Quirky</strong>: Laras isn’t just cute—her antics will leave you laughing and wanting more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full of Surprises</strong>: From helping you with daily tasks to asking for your attention, she’s as real as it gets!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person Immersion</strong><br>Experience the story through your character’s eyes and enjoy a lifelike perspective that puts you right in the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/5230121e0566b53f5f57c7fb2848f5a5.poster.avif?t=1743995851\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/5230121e0566b53f5f57c7fb2848f5a5.webm?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/5230121e0566b53f5f57c7fb2848f5a5.mp4?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Branching Storylines</strong><br>Your choices shape the narrative! Will you bond deeply with Laras, focus on your responsibilities, or explore the unexpected? Every decision unlocks unique interactions and endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/f11544815ce57448e00651cc308772b2.poster.avif?t=1743995851\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/f11544815ce57448e00651cc308772b2.webm?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/f11544815ce57448e00651cc308772b2.mp4?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Gameplay</strong><br>Manage your daily life while Laras brings chaos and sweetness to your world. Explore the environment, engage in heartfelt dialogues, and discover hidden surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Quality Visuals</strong><br>Stunning visuals bring Laras to life, ensuring every moment feels vivid and engaging.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"My Waifu Becomes Real\"</strong> is an immersive interactive visual novel that blurs the lines between fantasy and reality. Step into the life of an anime enthusiast whose dreams come true when Laras, his beloved waifu, becomes real and starts living with him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a story filled with humor, warmth, and heart-fluttering moments as you navigate the joys and challenges of living with a waifu who’s charming, quirky, and full of surprises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/882786b3861e6b0115414731ff05f04d.poster.avif?t=1743995851\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/882786b3861e6b0115414731ff05f04d.webm?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/882786b3861e6b0115414731ff05f04d.mp4?t=1743995851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet Laras<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468500/extras/aef005d297d275e4d6e9570d97c38cb4.avif?t=1743995851\" width=800 height=929 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sweet and Caring</strong>: Always ready to brighten your day with her infectious energy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playful and Quirky</strong>: Laras isn’t just cute—her antics will leave you laughing and wanting more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full of Surprises</strong>: From helping you with daily tasks to asking for your attention, she’s as real as it gets!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-Person I